
.card.mb-4
  .card-body
    %h2.card-title.d-flex.justify-content-between.mb-4
      %span projects
      = link_to new_project_path, class: "btn btn-primary" do
        %i.fa.fa-plus

    جاری سائٹ:
    - @projects.each do |project|
      -if !project.finished
        =link_to project do
          .card
            .card-body
              %h4.card-title
                = project.name
              %p.d-inline
                = project.address
              %footer.blockquote-footer
                ( #{project.size} )

.card
  .card-body
    ختم سائٹ:
    - @projects.each do |project|
      -if project.finished
        =link_to project do
          .card
            .card-body
              %h4.card-title
                = project.name
              %p
                = project.address